        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  NSAID na√Øve during the last month;

          -  absence of drugs, nutrient supplements, probiotics, prebiotics and synbiotics that
             might interfere with microbial homeostasis for all participants;

          -  no past history of gastrointestinal bleeding or ulcers;

